{"type":"message","id":"64bb1a31","parentId":"a399706e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:39:23.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我查找PPT生成相关的skill。我需要检查是否有现成的skill可以安装使用。\n\n作为子agent，我需要完成这个任务。我应该搜索已有的skill列表，或者搜索相关的技能。我可以查看可用的技能列表，但这里只显示了可用技能，我需要查看完整的技能库。\n\n让我先搜索一下PPT相关的技能。我可以使用web_search来搜索，或者用clawhub技能来搜索技能库。clawhub技能是用于搜索、安装、更新和发布agent skills的。我可以使用clawhub来搜索技能。\n\n首先，我需要读取clawhub技能的SKILL.md文件，了解如何使用它。然后，我可以用它来搜索PPT相关的技能。\n\n让我先读取clawhub技能的SKILL.md文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0ff358c5d72b4579a034e9ac","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":8703,"output":373,"cacheRead":110,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9186,"cost":{"input":0.00078327,"output":0.00010816999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00000495,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00089639}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773992361054}}
{"type":"message","id":"242c0f7d","parentId":"64bb1a31","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:39:23.940Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0ff358c5d72b4579a034e9ac","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773992363937}}
