{"type":"message","id":"a7235fc1","parentId":"243e5522","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:39:44.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"速率限制了。让我稍等一下再试，或者先看看已搜索到的结果。我已经找到了几个PPT相关的技能。让我查看一下这些技能的详细信息。\n\n首先，让我看看`ppt-generator`这个技能的详细信息。我可以使用`clawhub info`命令来查看技能详情。但根据SKILL.md，似乎没有`info`命令。让我试试`clawhub search`并查看更多结果，或者使用`clawhub list`来查看已安装的技能。\n\n实际上，我需要帮助用户安装PPT生成相关的技能。我已经找到了几个候选：\n\n1. `ppt-generator` - 将用户讲稿一键生成乔布斯风极简科技感竖屏HTML演示稿\n2. `ai-ppt-generate` - AI PPT generate\n3. `ppt` - PPT\n4. `dragon-ppt-maker` - PPT制作\n5. `ppt-generator-1` - Ppt Generator 1\n6. `zeelin-auto-ppt` - ZeeLin Auto-PPT\n7. `notebooklm-ppt` - NotebookLM PPT\n8. `auto-ppt` - Auto Ppt\n9. `ppt-translator` - PPT Translator\n10. `ppt-outline` - Ppt Outline\n11. `ai-presentation-maker` - AI Presentation Maker\n12. `generate-presentation` - Generate Presentation\n13. `afrexai-presentation-mastery` - Presentation Mastery\n14. `presentation-html-generator-skill` - revol-presentation-html-generator\n15. `presentation` - Presentation\n16. `presentation-generation` - Presentation Generation\n17. `recipe-create-presentation` - Recipe Create Presentation\n\n我应该为用户提供这些技能的列表，并推荐最合适的。根据描述，`ppt-generator`似乎是最直接的，因为它专门用于生成PPT，而且描述中提到了\"一键生成乔布斯风极简科技感竖屏HTML演示稿\"。\n\n不过，我还需要确认这些技能是否可用，以及安装方法。让我再尝试搜索一下\"ppt generator\"看看。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b2642dd5480e487bbfa093b5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search \"ppt generator\" --limit 5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":70,"output":922,"cacheRead":9992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10984,"cost":{"input":0.0000063,"output":0.00026738,"cacheRead":0.00044964,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00072332}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773992379369}}
